      <h3>Do you offer emergency plumbing in Placerville, CA?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Call <a href="tel:+15304992223">530-499-2223</a> to check availability for urgent plumbing issues.</p>

      <h3>How do I know if a clog is a main line issue?</h3>
      <p>If multiple drains are slow or backing up at the same time, the restriction may be in a branch line or main line rather than a single fixture.</p>

      <h3>Can you repair or replace water heaters?</h3>
      <p>Yes. We can troubleshoot common hot water issues and help you decide whether repair or replacement is best for long-term reliability.</p>

      <h3>What’s the best way to prevent recurring drain clogs?</h3>
      <p>Avoid repeated chemical cleaners, address buildup early, and use prevention habits that match fixture use. If clogs keep returning, diagnostics are recommended.</p>
